sql: SELECT COUNT(Classroom), AVG(Classroom), FirstName, Classroom FROM teachers WHERE  Classroom > 71 GROUP BY Classroom HAVING MIN(Classroom) > 93
SELECT list.Classroom FROM list AS l JOIN list ON list.LastName = l.LastName WHERE  l.Grade = 18
SELECT MAX(Grade), Grade FROM list WHERE  Classroom > 26
SELECT c.Grade, c.LastName, c.FirstName FROM list AS c ORDER BY c.Grade ASC LIMIT 3

SELECT LastName, LastName, FirstName FROM list WHERE Grade BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR LastName <= (SELECT SUM(LastName) FROM teachers WHERE Classroom BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Classroom <= 10) GROUP BY FirstName LIMIT 10
SELECT COUNT(Grade), Classroom FROM list WHERE Classroom BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Classroom >= 54 ORDER BY Classroom ASC
SELECT p.FirstName FROM list AS p ORDER BY p.FirstName ASC
SELECT i.FirstName FROM teachers AS i WHERE i.Classroom BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND LastName NOT IN (SELECT LastName FROM teachers AS w WHERE  w.Classroom >= 21 LIMIT 9)
SELECT q.Classroom, q.LastName FROM teachers AS q WHERE  q.Classroom >= 7
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT g.FirstName), g.LastName FROM list AS g WHERE  g.Grade > 85 OR FirstName NOT IN (SELECT FirstName FROM teachers WHERE  Classroom <= 10) ORDER BY g.LastName DESC
SELECT Classroom, Classroom FROM teachers WHERE LastName NOT IN (SELECT LastName FROM list WHERE  Classroom <= 76)
SELECT y.Classroom FROM list AS y WHERE  y.Grade > 50
SELECT SUM(l.Classroom), l.Classroom, l.FirstName FROM teachers AS l WHERE  l.Classroom >= 88 GROUP BY l.FirstName HAVING MIN(l.Classroom) >= 83
SELECT Classroom, Grade, FirstName FROM list WHERE  Grade = 89 GROUP BY FirstName HAVING COUNT(Classroom) <= 70 ORDER BY FirstName ASC
SELECT LastName FROM teachers WHERE Classroom <= (SELECT MIN(Classroom) FROM list WHERE  Classroom >= 61)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT f.Classroom), f.Grade, f.FirstName FROM list AS f WHERE FirstName = (SELECT MAX(FirstName) FROM list) LIMIT 10
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT v.FirstName) FROM teachers AS v WHERE  v.Classroom <= 17
SELECT Classroom FROM teachers WHERE  Classroom < 5 ORDER BY Classroom DESC
SELECT SUM(y.Classroom), y.LastName FROM teachers AS y WHERE y.Classroom BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  y.Classroom > 54 ORDER BY y.LastName DESC
